# Custom Focus Tracking Options

Follow the steps below to adjust settings for Set 6.

1. Select **AF-C CUSTOM SETTINGS > SET 6 CUSTOM**.

   !AF-C Custom Settings Menu

2. Press the selector up or down to highlight items and rotate the front command dial to change. To reset settings to their original values, press the reset button.

3. Press **DISP/BACK** when settings are complete.
